My setup:

Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS (Jammy) running on Windows 11 wsl
ROS2 @ rolling distribution
roslib.js @ ros2 branch ( commit 6a63a03 )
rosbridge_suite @ ros2-actions branch ( commit 692f41a )
ROS_PYTHON_VERSION=3
